  "detailed_description": "Catch the Vandal is an multiplayer game for you to play with 2-8 friends or other people where players within a city will act as both police officers and vandals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/c8fca5e4375f78d96ba4ae893a32e7ee.poster.avif?t=1720808362\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/c8fca5e4375f78d96ba4ae893a32e7ee.webm?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/c8fca5e4375f78d96ba4ae893a32e7ee.mp4?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POLICE OFFICERS</h2>The police officers' goal is to identify the vandals who are vandalizing the city among the citizens. But be careful not to rush into arresting everyone, as your badges may run out, and you'll need to return to the police station to reload.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/1468790c32f1e8f51a479d0c960fa6f4.poster.avif?t=1720808362\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/1468790c32f1e8f51a479d0c960fa6f4.webm?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/1468790c32f1e8f51a479d0c960fa6f4.mp4?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VANDALS</h2>The vandals' objective is to blend in among the citizens and vandalize the city, with the objects that can be vandalized indicated by stars. But be cautious, once the police officers apprehend you, you'll rely on your teammates to win.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/2d6b87c3500584219b46aea362e41bb2.poster.avif?t=1720808362\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/2d6b87c3500584219b46aea362e41bb2.webm?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/2d6b87c3500584219b46aea362e41bb2.mp4?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE STYLES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/8952489860f7ce0d48b89c10e2a5ca20.poster.avif?t=1720808362\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/8952489860f7ce0d48b89c10e2a5ca20.webm?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920600/extras/8952489860f7ce0d48b89c10e2a5ca20.mp4?t=1720808362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAVE FUN!</h2>It's a simple game where the first to accomplish their objectives wins.<br><br>Gather your friends and have fun disguising, deceiving, chasing, and laughing in the end with Catch the Vandal.<br><br>",
